parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Cracked Dashboard and Airbag Safety Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracked dashboard can compromise the airbag system, leading to improper deployment or failure to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: particularly on the passenger side near the airbag location
and dashboard material separating or breaking apart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard near the airbag area can potentially cause the airbag to deploy improperly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: especially on the passenger side near the airbag area
which can spread and worsen over time. In some cases
the airbag warning light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become inoperable, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience sudden loss of power
or warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and gearbox can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become inoperable, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience difficulties shifting gears
accompanied by unusual vibrations or warning lights on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and jerking can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become inoperable, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience sudden jerking or slipping of the transmission
or warning lights on the dashboard.
